Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Intention Planning Module Stub
Provides comprehensive intention planning with hierarchical decomposition and temporal reasoning
Enables HTN planning, constraint solving, and adaptive planning strategies
:End Note

Type PlanningType is Union containing:
    "hierarchical_planning",
    "temporal_planning",
    "conditional_planning",
    "reactive_planning",
    "continuous_planning",
    "multi_agent_planning",
    "constraint_planning",
    "probabilistic_planning",
    "adaptive_planning",
    "meta_planning"

Type IntentionPlan is Dictionary with:
    plan_id as String
    intention_ref as String
    planning_type as PlanningType
    plan_structure as Dictionary
    execution_steps as List[Dictionary]
    resource_allocation as Dictionary
    temporal_schedule as Dictionary
    contingency_plans as List[Dictionary]
    constraint_specifications as Dictionary
    success_conditions as Dictionary
    failure_recovery as Dictionary
    adaptation_triggers as List[Dictionary]
    plan_metrics as Dictionary
    plan_metadata as Dictionary

Type PlanningStep is Dictionary with:
    step_id as String
    step_type as String
    step_description as String
    preconditions as List[Dictionary]
    actions as List[Dictionary]
    postconditions as List[Dictionary]
    resource_requirements as Dictionary
    temporal_constraints as Dictionary
    success_criteria as Dictionary
    failure_conditions as Dictionary
    alternative_steps as List[String]
    monitoring_points as List[Dictionary]
    step_metadata as Dictionary

Type PlanningContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    environmental_state as Dictionary
    available_resources as Dictionary
    temporal_constraints as Dictionary
    external_constraints as Dictionary
    agent_capabilities as Dictionary
    collaboration_requirements as Dictionary
    uncertainty_factors as Dictionary
    risk_assessment as Dictionary
    planning_preferences as Dictionary
    context_metadata as Dictionary

Type PlanningResult is Dictionary with:
    result_id as String
    intention_ref as String
    generated_plan as IntentionPlan
    planning_analysis as Dictionary
    feasibility_assessment as Dictionary
    optimality_analysis as Dictionary
    risk_analysis as Dictionary
    alternative_plans as List[IntentionPlan]
    execution_recommendations as Dictionary
    monitoring_recommendations as Dictionary
    adaptation_recommendations as Dictionary
    result_confidence as Float

Type PlanningEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine_id as String
    planning_algorithms as List[PlanningAlgorithm]
    decomposition_strategies as List[DecompositionStrategy]
    constraint_solvers as List[ConstraintSolver]
    optimization_engines as List[OptimizationEngine]
    planning_metrics as PlanningMetrics
    planning_validation as PlanningValidation

Type DecompositionStrategy is Dictionary with:
    strategy_id as String
    strategy_type as String
    decomposition_rules as List[DecompositionRule]
    hierarchy_builder as HierarchyBuilder
    strategy_metrics as StrategyMetrics
    strategy_validation as StrategyValidation

Type TemporalRequirements is Dictionary with:
    requirements_id as String
    temporal_constraints as List[TemporalConstraint]
    deadline_requirements as DeadlineRequirements
    scheduling_preferences as SchedulingPreferences
    temporal_metrics as TemporalMetrics

Type RiskAnalysis is Dictionary with:
    analysis_id as String
    risk_factors as List[RiskFactor]
    risk_assessment as RiskAssessment
    mitigation_strategies as List[MitigationStrategy]
    risk_metrics as RiskMetrics

Type OptimizationCriteria is Dictionary with:
    criteria_id as String
    optimization_objectives as List[OptimizationObjective]
    constraint_weights as Dictionary
    optimization_algorithm as String
    convergence_criteria as ConvergenceCriteria

Type AdaptationContext is Dictionary with:
    context_id as String
    adaptation_triggers as List[AdaptationTrigger]
    adaptation_constraints as List[AdaptationConstraint]
    adaptation_preferences as AdaptationPreferences
    adaptation_metrics as AdaptationMetrics

Process called "create_intention_planning_engine" that takes engine_config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_intention_plan" that takes planning_engine as Dictionary and intention as Dictionary and planning_context as PlanningContext returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_hierarchical_planning" that takes intention as Dictionary and planning_context as PlanningContext and decomposition_strategy as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_temporal_planning" that takes intention as Dictionary and planning_context as PlanningContext and temporal_requirements as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_contingency_plans" that takes primary_plan as IntentionPlan and risk_analysis as Dictionary and planning_context as PlanningContext returns Dictionary
Process called "optimize_intention_plan" that takes intention_plan as IntentionPlan and optimization_criteria as Dictionary and planning_context as PlanningContext returns Dictionary
Process called "adapt_intention_plan" that takes intention_plan as IntentionPlan and adaptation_context as Dictionary and plan_state as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "generate_intention_plan_id" that takes nothing returns String
Process called "determine_optimal_planning_type" that takes planning_analysis as Dictionary and planning_context as PlanningContext returns PlanningType
Process called "generate_contingency_id" that takes nothing returns String 